I want to talk about the "NFT". It's a totally new technologie who has taken a big place in the internet cause of all the story of succes they have made, but i want to talk more about the impact of the NFT on The link bewteen human and internet. So "NFT" is the acronyme of "Non-fungible token" and its a technologie using the systeme of the blockchain that can be explain has a big big data base that anybody can use, so everyone can trust the blockchain beacause its 100% see-throught. And the NFT take place in the blockchain like a document who can certified that somebody is the owner of something that is not in the real world but in internet. So now that the NFT has been introduce we can talk about the consequence. First of all, the NFT has been populare thanks to the world of the digital art who has take the NFT for a tool that can monetize your art, so we have seen artiste sell NFT for 100K$ who have take all the place in the media but we still have NFT which have low price like 30$. But the NFT is more than just a certificat for PNG on the internet cause NFT can be anything and a lot of big thinker in the world say that in 10 years NfT are gonna be everwhere because she can be anything. Lets have an example, you want to take 2 place for the prefer artiste show of your daughter, so you go on internet with your etherum wallet (the crytocurrencie use for buying NFT) and the ticket are in a NFT modele so you buy them and you receive the NFT code that proves that you bought them. When you go to the show with your daughter, they ask you the NFT code, they check on the blockain who has buy the ticket, they see your number so they now sure that you have buy the tickets and you can go and have a wonderful show with your lovelly daughter. That is one example one thousand of thousand possible. In a close futur, NFT can bee anything like plane ticket, only possible acces to an event maybe your littel baker in your city want to make bread in exchange of NFT. We can see that NFT is a possible new type of exchange for everybody in the world that cant bee manipulate by state or the inflation cause nobody have te power on it.
 My point of view on the NFT is a good new technologie. If we take apart the idea that NFT is just a dumb way to use the money of rich people for make them buying things that are not real and just a picture of a stylish monkey. We can see all the potential of the NFT, its making hundred of projet everyday that goes from art to ecologicall projet. But NfT is not 100% clean dont let me say that, We know that NFT is polluting the world cause its increasing the carbone impact who is already so big and of course the NFT are like 10000% capitalist and liberal and that is not for sure totally great.
